N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 9006.2 - Documentary provisions

State Regulations

Every contract or agreement entered into by the board or a
deferred compensation committee in respect of a plan shall contain a provision
that the agreement or contract is subject to the plan and to this Subtitle, and
that such plan and this Subtitle are made a part thereof. Notes
